                    <scriptDesc>
                        <scriptNote script="uncialis">
                            <p>The text of the calender and the tables on <locus from="1r" to="10v">ff. 1r-10v</locus>is written in uncial in red and green.</p>
                        </scriptNote>
                        <scriptNote script="carolmin">
                            <p>The argumenta on <locus from="11r" to="19r"> f. 11r-19r</locus> are written in tiny Caroline minuscule.</p>
